{"tid":87524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英稱自己非普京　無考慮亦沒有計劃再參選特首","createTime":"2017-01-20T01:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T06:06:37.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e68ae286ea71ae78f49cd52ee08aa51f5dfd719","tid":87524,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"行政長官梁振英出席本台英文節目時被問到日後會否再參選特首，他笑言自己並非俄羅斯總統普京，並無考慮亦沒有計劃再參選。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英說，過去40年都在國家及香港擔任公職，至於卸任後會如何，他說，會做可以做到的事，未來5個月會盡力做好餘下工作。<br />\n<br />\n對於特首選舉，梁振英說，如果民主派亦派人參選，可以為香港帶來真選擇；即使有5、6人參選，亦並非不好，相信有助完善選舉制度。<br />\n<br />\n被問到銅鑼灣書店事件會否破壞港人對一國兩制的信心，梁振英認為是有影響，但相信已恢復，強調當局會改善兩地通報機制。"},{"pid":"a88ce74c13f3ee557f43656bac3e3cc158c54b66","tid":87524,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:38:52.000Z","msg":"咁臭串?"},{"pid":"d46ef51d0010e35a8ce1cf56e676fd8e68198fa1","tid":87524,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678625c43a5a8e0ae636524d11251da54ebaeb96","tid":87524,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"你話普京會唔會損害中國同俄羅斯嘅關係？"},{"pid":"fd7a2c59d82f4c504743e26f1bb870a7a1c38a38","tid":87524,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"收撚皮喇你狗嚟嫁炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n揾普京同自己比想笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1905149c78e1f786bca9772728dfa91c2b67e3","tid":87524,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:52:22.000Z","msg":"用特首呢個職位同總統比<br />\n香港